data.description: Take A Look At This Charming 2- Bed, 2-Bath Single-Family Home Nestled In A Peaceful Neighborhood. Embrace Two Flourishing Mango Trees On A 6,000 Sq Ft Lot. Enjoy Cooking In A  New Kitchen Stainless Appliances & Soft Close Cabinets And Drawers . Brand New Remodeled Bathrooms, Lots Of Natural Light W/ Freshly Painted Exterior & Interior. Enjoy The HUGE Family Room W/ Wall To Wall Windows. Large Laundry Room That Leads To The Garage. LOW HOA MONTHLY FEE $65. Property Comes W/ Storm Shutters On EVERY Window.  4 Point & Wind Mitigation Completed On 10/19/23, 30 Year Architectural Roof Replaced In 2003 W/ 10 Years Remaining Life Span, Electrical Panel Replaced in 2023, AC Replaced In 2021, Water Heater Replaced in 2019. Use Showing Time To Schedule Appt
